title: Install Groovy LSP in Lunarvim or Neovim
tags: @zettel _method lunarvim groovy mason
roam-id: d7a638a4-9a47-4125-90ee-9bfb329e9653
type: text/markdown

- install java on your system.
  - [[Install Java on Nixos]] or [[Install Java on Ubuntu or Debian]]
- launch `lvim`
- do `:Mason`
- search \"groovy\"
- navigate to `groovy-language-server`
- press `i` for install
